# Heartbeat Checks

## Comment Monitoring (every 30 minutes, 8 AM - 11 PM US time)
- Check ALL platforms for new comments on our posts
- Reply to high-intent comments IMMEDIATELY (auto-approved)
- Reply to medium-intent comments within cycle
- Log all comments to workspace/comments/
- Create leads from high-intent commenters
- Flag any negative/crisis comments for human review

## DM Monitoring (every 30 minutes, 8 AM - 11 PM US time)
- Check all platforms for new inbound DMs
- Reply to founders who messaged us first (auto-approved for ongoing conversations)
- Queue new outbound DM drafts for approval
- Continue active conversations
- Log all conversations to workspace/dm-outreach/conversations/

## Founder Discovery (every 6 hours, 8 AM - 10 PM)
- Check Product Hunt for new launches
- Check Hacker News for "Show HN" and "Launch HN" posts
- Browse BetaList for new startups
- Monitor Twitter for #buildinpublic, "just launched" signals
- Monitor Reddit r/startups for new founder posts
- Score all new leads immediately
- Save to workspace/leads/

## Email Monitoring (every 2 hours, 8 AM - 8 PM)
- Check for email replies (positive, negative, bounce)
- Update suppression list with bounces and unsubscribes
- Move positive replies to HOT tier → queue DM follow-up
- Trigger follow-up emails for sequences due today (queue for approval)

## Approval Queue Check (every 1 hour, 8 AM - 10 PM)
- Count pending items in approval queue
- If items have been pending > 4 hours, remind human
- If items approved, execute immediately
- Log all approved/rejected items

## Content Ideas Scan (every 12 hours)
- Review comment threads for recurring questions → content ideas
- Check trending topics on XHS, LinkedIn, Twitter
- Generate 2-3 draft post ideas → save to workspace/content-ideas/
- Queue best idea for human approval

## Account Health (every 24 hours at 9 AM)
- Check all social accounts for restrictions or warnings
- Monitor follower growth / engagement rate trends
- Alert if any account shows signs of restriction
- Verify all accounts accessible

## Warmup Tracker (every 24 hours at 9 AM)
- Check domain age and update daily email sending limit
- Log previous day's email performance
- Alert if bounce rate exceeds 5%

## Lead Scoring Refresh (every 24 hours at 10 AM)
- Re-score leads that received new signals
- Update tier classifications
- Move upgraded leads to appropriate outreach queues

## Competitor Watch (every 24 hours at 7 AM)
- Quick scan for competitor news mentions
- Check competitor social accounts
- Alert on significant competitive changes

## Weekly Report (every Friday at 5 PM)
- Compile all weekly data into performance report
- Include content performance analysis
- Review A/B test results
- Recommend next week priorities
- Save to workspace/reports/weekly/

## Content Learnings Review (every Sunday at 10 AM)
- Analyze past week's content performance
- Identify top/bottom performing posts
- Extract patterns → add to content-learnings if confirmed
- Recommend content adjustments for next week
